[CHALLENGE]
Using the unfinished php app from above
1. Create your own database and complete the task/feature list
CRUD functions for DB
CREATE
 DONE - create users (register)
 DONE - create restaurants (add restaurant)
READ
 DOOOONE- - search users
 DONE - - user login
DONE - read restaurant table (display restaurants)
DONE - - search restaurants
UPDATE
DOOOOONE- update user (update profile)
DOOOOONE-update restaurant (update restaurant)
DELETE
- delete restaurant
2. Create database tables as follows:
LIST of DB Tables
restaurants table
- name
- location
- type of food - array
- price range
- picture
Users table
- email
- password
3. Style index.php according to https://dribbble.com/shots/3226909-Food-UI-Kit#shot-description
3.1. Add App Name and Logo
3.2. Change Colors
3.3. Add background image
4. Use php file upload to upload restaurant pictures
5. Use https://www.cssscript.com/demo/creating-a-star-rating-widget-with-pure-html-css/ to replace the Price range dropdown. Change the icon to Dollars or yen (edited) 